> """[FR-18] Intent Router + Dialogue State Tracker (DST) — 7-state FSM.
  
> Acceptance criteria:
>   - ConversationState enum: IDLE, INTENT_DETECTED, SLOT_FILLING, AWAITING_CONFIRMATION,
>     PROCESSING, RESOLVED, ESCALATED
>   - DialogueSlot(name, value, required, prompt) — required slot missing triggers prompt
>   - DialogueState fields: conversation_id, current_state, primary_intent, sub_intents,
>     slots dict, turn_count, last_updated
>   - DialogueState.transition(new_state) immutable: returns new DialogueState,
>     turn_count += 1, last_updated = UTC now
>   - DialogueState.missing_slots() returns required slots where value is None
>   - State transitions: IDLE→INTENT_DETECTED, INTENT_DETECTED→PROCESSING|SLOT_FILLING,
>     SLOT_FILLING→AWAITING_CONFIRMATION|ESCALATED, AWAITING_CONFIRMATION→PROCESSING|SLOT_FILLING,
>     PROCESSING→RESOLVED|ESCALATED, ESCALATED→RESOLVED
  
> Citations: SRS.md:110-133, SAD.md:363-399
> """
  
